com.github.alexmojaki.caseclasses

Class AbstractResultBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.alexmojaki.caseclasses.AbstractResultBuilder
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ResultBuilder

    public abstract class AbstractResultBuilder
extends Object
implements ResultBuilder
    A skeleton to make implementing ResultBuilder easier. The implementations of add return the builder for chaining so that instead you should implement the void methods simpleAdd. The simpleAdd methods for primitive values delegate to simpleAdd(String, Object) so you need only override them if you wish to avoid autoboxing for efficiency.
